CORRELATIONS BETWEEN DIFFERENT THINGS:
 - Claiming a square allows for their to be more room to develop. Developing GDP is multiplied by the squares that you own.
 - Developing GDP allows for a stronger economy, so on you receive a boost of ONE TROOP for every 10K GDP.
 - Training troops makes claiming squares easier when attacking.
 
These methods ensure that a player who only plays with a hawkish eye will lose, and so will a pacifist who stays in their zone and doesn't move.
 
They reward a balanced player who takes all of their moves into account.